summary: This mod adds 22 more high elves to the game, per a user request. The majority are marriage candidates, unique, and are spread across the province. No DLC required.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 20 more high elves to the base Skyrim continent. Each of these high elves are unique and are spread throughout the province. Below are a list of each of them and where you might find them (since a few of them wander on the roads):

Dark Brotherhood:

Ancelmaellith Highious - He is a member of the Dark Brotherhood (Can Marry)

Niryrie Chaeaere - She is a member of the Dark Brotherhood (Can Marry)

Dawnstar:

Eraandilnalus Khraemorinh - He is a mercenary for hire staying at the inn (Can Marry)

Mirielinwae Gaeore - She is a mage staying at the inn (Can Marry)

Ivarstead:

Ravermend Tahromor - She is a mercenary for hire staying at the inn (Can Marry)

Morthal:

Caraionhnilian Alkinire - He is a bard in Morthal (Can Marry)

Nanndilnalus Larenhthaer - He is a guard for the city of Morthal

Riften:

Tilnaro Jorious - He is a member of the Thieves Guild (Can Marry)

Viraena Chamoth - She is a member of the Thieves Guild (Can Marry)

Riverwood:

Gyrnonl Aedus - He is a mage staying at the inn (Can Marry)

Solitude:

Anadildorume Kororin - He is a member of the Bard's College (Can Marry)

Taaronirya Grayfhar - She is a member of the Bard's College (Can Marry)

Whiterun:

Kariwen Loraethahl - She is a bard in Whiterun (Can Marry)

Peloril Elsinwatch - He is a member of the Companions (can marry)

Psyeya Stormious - She is a member of the Companions (can marry)

Winterhold:

Ardana Chamorin - She is a member of the College of Winterhold (Can Marry)

Calwe Gaethiath - She is a member of the College of Winterhold (Can Marry)

Liliarume Anaedihle - She is a guard for the city of Winterhold

Lylintiersanon Stormiuth - He is a member of the College of Winterhold (Can Marry)

Umbreanaro Silinore - He is a member of the College of Winterhold (Can Marry)

Wilderness:

Hessande Adaire - She is a wandering mage (Can Marry)

Ravldur Elsinaerith - He is a wandering mage (Can Marry)

Changelog:
V1.2:
-Added 2 NPCS to the Companions
V1.1:
-Changed the voice type of all the male bards to have the correct voice type.
V1:
-The initial release.

Known Bugs:
None at this time.
